data.title: Things to do in Prague
data.meta_description: Things to do  in Prague (CZ) - Foot traffic data and popular times
data.text:
Prague Castle is most popular around 12 PM on Saturdays. Visitors usually stay up to 3 hours here. It's most quiet on Mondays.

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.

Old Town Square is most popular around 3 PM on Saturdays. It's most quiet on Tuesdays.

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.

St. Vitus Cathedral is most popular around 12 PM on Saturdays. It's most quiet on Mondays.

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.

Prague Astronomical Clock is most popular around 2 PM on Saturdays. Visitors usually stay up to 1 hour here. It's most quiet on Tuesdays.

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.

PALLADIUM is most popular around 3 PM on Saturdays. Visitors usually stay 20 min to 1,5 hr here. It's most quiet on Sundays.

PALLADIUM je moderním nákupním centrem s nejširší nabídkou obchodů, restaurací a služeb uprostřed historické Prahy. Na 5 podlažích nabízí zákazníkům 200 prodejen, restaurací a kaváren. V podzemí na 3 podlažích pak 700 parkovacích míst. Citlivé propojení historických prvků s moderní architekturou vytváří jedinečnou atmosféru, která činí z nakupování v PALLADIU opravdový zážitek! #YourBest Style #PalladiumPraha

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.

Prague Zoo is most popular around 1 PM on Saturdays. Visitors usually stay 3-5,5 hours here. It's most quiet on Tuesdays.

For more info visit the website or checkout Google Maps.
